msgstr "Označuje, kaj naj se prikaže pod glavnim območjem."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "Neither airspace nor terrain is used for route planning."
msgstr ""
"Ni uporabljajo zračne oznake ali zemljepisne značilnosti za načrtovanje "
"poti."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Routes will avoid terrain."
msgstr "Potni so preprečeni od zemljišča."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "Routes will avoid airspace."
msgstr "Potni so preprečeni od zračnih oznak."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "Routes will avoid airspace and terrain."
msgstr "Potni so preprečeni od zračnih oznak in zemljišča."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:94
msgid "Route mode"
msgstr "Potna način"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:97
msgid "Route climb"
msgstr "Potna vzpon"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:98
msgid ""
"When enabled and MC is positive, route planning allows climbs between the "
"aircraft location and destination."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočeno in MC je pozitiven, načrtovanje poti omogoča vzpon med "
"letalnim lokacijo in ciljno destinacijo."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:103
msgid "Route ceiling"
msgstr "Potna višina"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:104
msgid ""
"When enabled, route planning climbs are limited to ceiling defined by "
"greater of current aircraft altitude plus 500 m and the thermal ceiling. If "
"disabled, climbs are unlimited."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočeno, načrtovanje poti vzponov omejuje na višino, ki jo določi "
"večja od trenutne letalske višine plus 500 m in talnih višin. Če je "
"izklopljena, so vzponi neomejeni."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reach calculations disabled."
msgstr "Izračun hitrosti preprečen."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Straight"
msgstr "Pravokoten"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "The reach is from straight line paths from the glider."
msgstr "Razdalja se določi s pravokotnimi poti od gliderska."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Turning"
msgstr "Premik"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "The reach is calculated allowing turns around terrain obstacles."
msgstr "Razdalja se izračuna, omogoča premik okoli zemljepisnih obremenitev."

#. Spacer
#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:122
msgid "Reach mode"
msgstr "Dose mode"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:123
msgid ""
"How calculations are performed of the reach of the glider with respect to "
"terrain."
msgstr "Kako se izračuna dosega gliderskega letala glede na relief."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Uses task glide polar."
msgstr "Izkorišča zadnji glidni polar."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:130
#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SafetyFactorsConfigPanel.cpp:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Safety MC"
msgstr "Varnostna MC"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Uses safety MacCready value."
msgstr "Izkorišča varnostna MacCready vrednost."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:135
msgid "Reach polar"
msgstr "Dosegn polar"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:136
msgid ""
"This determines the glide performance used in reach, landable arrival, abort"
" and alternate calculations."
msgstr ""
"To določa glidno sposobnost, uporabljano v dosegu, pristajalni prihod, "
"odločitve in alternativne računanje."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disables the reach display."
msgstr "Izklopi dosegov prikaz."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "Terrain line"
msgstr "Vključi teren"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draws a dashed line at the terrain glide reach."
msgstr "Vzorje za dosego gliderskega letala."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "Terrain shade"
msgstr "Vključi teren"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shades terrain outside glide reach."
msgstr "Osvetli relief zunaj dosega gliderskega letala."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working line"
msgstr "Delna linija"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draws a dashed line at the working glide reach."
msgstr "Vzorje za dosego gliderskega letala."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:149
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working line, terrain line"
msgstr "Delna linija, relief linija"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draws a dashed line at the working and terrain glide reaches."
msgstr "Vzorje za dosego in relief glidnih razmerij."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working line, terrain shade"
msgstr "Delna linija, relief osvetlitev"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draws a dashed line at working, and shade terrain, glide reaches."
msgstr "Delcijeva črta dela delovanje, in obarva relief, glidniške poti."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/RouteConfigPanel.cpp:156
msgid "Reach display"
msgstr "Dosega prikaz"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SafetyFactorsConfigPanel.cpp:47
#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/WaypointDisplayConfigPanel.cpp:112
msgid "Arrival height"
msgstr "Prihodek višine"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SafetyFactorsConfigPanel.cpp:48
msgid ""
"The height above terrain that the glider should arrive at for a safe "
"landing."
msgstr ""
"Višina nad reliefom, na katero se glider mora priti za varno pristajanje."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SafetyFactorsConfigPanel.cpp:53
msgid "Terrain height"
msgstr "Relief višine"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SafetyFactorsConfigPanel.cpp:54
msgid ""
"The height above terrain that the glider must clear during final glide."
msgstr "Višina nad reliefom, na katero se glider mora dvigniti v zadnji glid."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SafetyFactorsConfigPanel.cpp:60
#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SymbolsConfigPanel.cpp:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Simple"
msgstr "Opremljen"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SafetyFactorsConfigPanel.cpp:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The alternates will only be sorted by waypoint type (airport/outlanding "
"field) and arrival height."
msgstr ""
"Alternativne bodo samo sortirane po smeri letanja (letališče/izletišče) in "
"prihodek višine."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SafetyFactorsConfigPanel.cpp:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "The sorting will also take the current task direction into account."
msgstr "Sortiranje bo tudi upoštevalo trenutno naložbo."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SafetyFactorsConfigPanel.cpp:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Home"
msgstr "Dom"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SafetyFactorsConfigPanel.cpp:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The sorting will try to find landing options in the current direction to the"
" configured home waypoint."
msgstr ""
"Sortiranja bo pokusala najti možnosti za pristajanje v trenutni smeri do "
"konfiguracijskega doma."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SafetyFactorsConfigPanel.cpp:69
msgid "Alternates mode"
msgstr "Alternativna način"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SafetyFactorsConfigPanel.cpp:70
msgid ""
"Determines sorting of alternates in the alternates dialog and in abort mode."
msgstr ""
"Odločanje o sortiranju alternativ v dialogu alternativen in v odločitvi."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SafetyFactorsConfigPanel.cpp:73
msgid "Polar degradation"
msgstr "Polar degradacija"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SafetyFactorsConfigPanel.cpp:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A permanent polar degradation. 0% means no degradation, 50% indicates the "
"glider's sink rate is doubled."
msgstr ""
"Trajni polar degradacija. 0% pomeni, da ni degradacija, 50% kaže na to, da "
"se glider's sink rate dviga polovico."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SafetyFactorsConfigPanel.cpp:82
msgid "Auto bugs"
msgstr "Avtobugs"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SafetyFactorsConfigPanel.cpp:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, adds 1% to the bugs setting after each full hour while flying."
msgstr "Če enable, doda 1% do nastavka bugs po vsaki celotni uri med vožnjo."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SafetyFactorsConfigPanel.cpp:88
msgid ""
"The MacCready setting used, when safety MC is enabled for reach "
"calculations, in task abort mode and for determining arrival altitude at "
"airfields."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitev MacCready, uporabljena ko je varnostna MC omogočana za doseganje "
"računov, v načinu odpovedanja naloge in za določevanje višine pristajanja na"
" letališču."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SafetyFactorsConfigPanel.cpp:96
msgid "STF risk factor"
msgstr "STF tveganje"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SafetyFactorsConfigPanel.cpp:97
msgid ""
"The STF risk factor reduces the MacCready setting used to calculate speed to"
" fly as the glider gets low, in order to compensate for risk. Set to 0.0 for"
" no compensation, 1.0 scales MC linearly with current height (with reference"
" to height of the maximum climb). If considered, 0.3 is recommended."
msgstr ""
"Tveganje STF znižuje nastavitev MacCready, uporabljeno za izračun hitrosti "
"vožnje glidersa, ko se glider postane nizkega, da se kompenziruje tveganje. "
"Nastavite 0.0 za nekompenzacijo, 1.0 skalarje MC linearno s trenutnim višino"
" (z reference do višine največjega vzpona). Če je to potrebno, se priporoča "
"0.3."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SiteConfigPanel.cpp:45
msgid "XCSoar data path"
msgstr "XCSoar podatkovni poti"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SiteConfigPanel.cpp:45
msgid "Click to view full path"
msgstr "Kliknite, da vidite celotno pot"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SiteConfigPanel.cpp:49
msgid "Map database"
msgstr "Zemljevidna baza"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SiteConfigPanel.cpp:50
msgid ""
"The name of the file (.xcm) containing terrain, topography, and optionally "
"waypoints, their details and airspaces."
msgstr ""
"Imenik datoteke (.xcm), ki vsebuje relief, topografsko sliko in možnost "
"točk, njihove podrobnosti in zračne prostori."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SiteConfigPanel.cpp:55
msgid ""
"Primary waypoints files.  Supported file types are Cambridge/WinPilot files "
"(.dat), Zander files (.wpz) or SeeYou files (.cup)."
msgstr ""
"Osnovne točke. Podprane datoteke so Cambridge/WinPilot datoteke (.dat), "
"Zander datoteke (.wpz) ali SeeYou datoteke (.cup)."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SiteConfigPanel.cpp:61
msgid "Watched WPTs"
msgstr "Točke, ki jih je treba spremljati"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SiteConfigPanel.cpp:62
msgid ""
"Waypoint files containing special waypoints for which additional "
"computations like calculation of arrival height in map display always takes "
"place. Useful for waypoints like known reliable thermal sources (e.g. "
"powerplants) or mountain passes."
msgstr ""
"Točke, ki vsebujejo posebne točke, za katere se vedno izvaja dodatna "
"računanje, kot so izračun višine pristajanja na zemljišču v zemljevidu. "
"Uporabljene so točke, kot so znane zanesljive topne vire (npr. elektrarne) "
"ali planinske prehodi."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SiteConfigPanel.cpp:72
msgid "WPT A/F details"
msgstr "WPT A/F podrobnosti"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SiteConfigPanel.cpp:73
msgid ""
"The files may contain extracts from enroute supplements or other contributed"
" information about individual waypoints and airfields."
msgstr ""
"Datoteke lahko vsebujejo izvleči iz letnih dodatkov ali druge prispevane "
"informacije o individualnih točkah in letališču."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SiteConfigPanel.cpp:81
msgid ""
"List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or"
" deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair "
"(.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua)."
msgstr ""
"Seznam aktivnih zračnih prostorskih datotek. Uporabite gumb \"Dodaj\" in "
"\"Odstran\" za aktiviranje ali deaktiviranje zračnih prostorskih datotek. "
"Podprte datoteke so Openair (.txt /.air) in Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua)."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SiteConfigPanel.cpp:88
msgid "FLARM database"
msgstr "FLARM baza"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SiteConfigPanel.cpp:89
msgid ""
"The name of the file containing information about registered FLARM devices."
msgstr "Dokument, ki vsebuje informacije o registriranih FLARM napravah."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SiteConfigPanel.cpp:95
msgid ""
"Regional Atmospheric Soaring Prediction file providing weather forecasts for"
" soaring. Displays color-coded map overlays for thermal strength, boundary "
"layer winds, cloud cover, and other soaring-relevant parameters at various "
"forecast times throughout the day."
msgstr ""
"Regionalna atmosfera predikcija za vzletne letanje, ki nudi vremenske "
"napovedi za vzlaganje. Prikazuje barvo-odvisno mapovanje nadzorov za silo, "
"mehanizem v območju, oblaki in druge relevantne parametre za vzlaganje na "
"različnih napovednih časov v danu."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/SiteConfigPanel.cpp:104
msgid "The checklist file containing pre-flight and other checklists."
