#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:463
#, no-c-format
msgid "Speed dolphin"
msgstr "Hitrost delfin"

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Instantaneous MacCready speed-to-fly, making use of netto vario calculations"
" to determine dolphin cruise speed on the glider's current track. In cruise "
"flight mode, this speed-to-fly is calculated for maintaining altitude. In "
"final glide mode, this speed-to-fly is calculated for descent. In climb "
"mode, this switches to the speed for minimum sink at the current load factor"
" (if an accelerometer is connected). When Block mode speed-to-fly is "
"selected, this InfoBox displays the MacCready speed."
msgstr ""
"Instantaneous MacCready hitrost za vzlet, uporabljajoč netto vario računanje"
" za določevanje delfin krcalne hitrosti na trenutnem glidnem poti. V "
"krcalnem letni režimu se hitrost za vzlet izračuna za ohranjanje višine. V "
"zadnji gledanje režimu se hitrost za vzlet izračuna za padanje. V vzponu "
"režimu se hitrost za vzlet spreminja v hitrost za minimalno padanje pri "
"trenutnem teži (če je akcelerometer povezan). Ko je izbran način bloka "
"hitrost za vzlet, ta InfoBox prikazuje MacCready hitrost."

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:471
#, no-c-format
msgid "Netto vario"
msgstr "Neto Vario"

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:472
#, no-c-format
msgid "Netto"
msgstr "Neto"

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:473
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Instantaneous vertical speed of air-mass, equal to vario value less the "
"glider's estimated sink rate. Best used if airspeed, accelerometers and "
"vario are connected, otherwise calculations are based on GPS measurements "
"and wind estimates."
msgstr ""
"Instantaneous vertikala hitrost zračne mas, enako vrsti vario vrednosti "
"minus glidniško ocenjeno padanje. Najbolj uporabna, če je hitrost zraka, "
"akcelerometer in vario povezani, sicer računanje temelji na GPS merjenju in "
"ocenah tega."

